title: LIX: Odysseus and a Sea of Suitors' Blood (The Odyssey Part 12)
itunes:title: LIX: Odysseus and a Sea of Suitors' Blood (The Odyssey Part 12)
itunes:subtitle: Time's up, suitors.
description:
Odysseus is fed up, it's time for the suitors to die.


CW/TW: far too many Greek myths involve assault. Given it's fiction, and typically involves gods and/or monsters, I'm not as deferential as I would be were I referencing the real thing.


Sources: The Odyssey, translated by Emily Wilson.
